import jax.numpy as jnp

def generated_fn(x0, x1):
    v0 = jnp.maximum(x1, x0)
    v1 = jnp.add(x1, v0)
    v2 = jnp.maximum(x1, v1)
    v3 = jnp.exp(v2)
    v4 = jnp.add(v0, v0)
    v5 = jnp.tanh(v0)
    v6 = jnp.maximum(v5, v4)
    v7 = jnp.subtract(v6, v1)
